# General configuraton for yt-dlp

## Include Subtitles

--embed-subs
--sub-langs "en,zh,zh-CN,zh-Hans,ja,de"
--sub-format best

## Download-diirectory and filename

-o ~/Downloads/%(channel)s_%(playlist_title)s_%(title)s

## thumbnail

--embed-thumbnail

## Metadata

--embed-metadata

## Audio

--audio-format opus
--audio-quality 0

## Browser-Cookies

--cookies-from-browser firefox
